description:
@Rares No problem dude, the more people we have transcribing the better, perhaps you could add me on discord so we can contribute together if you want 
Discord Tag: Strigiformes#0599

It seems like the vocal track didn't change to an oboe and is stuck on the clarinet still, this revision changes that hopefully.

For some reason in Guitar Pro it bugs out when switching gp8 or gp7 files and converting them to gp5 files causing them to revert instrument changes. So I fixed this by creating a new track and selecting the instrument, in this case the oboe, and in doing this I copied over the notes from the other vocal track (the clarinet track) and then you export it to a gp5 file, this seems to work for some reason, the project file might be just cursed for no reason.
